[iamf][Rule #23] id: assert-base-enhanced-profile-restrictions
Section 4.3
Base-Enhanced Profile restrictions:
- There SHALL be at least one Mix Presentation OBU for at most 28 Audio Elements.
- The sum of channels across all Audio Elements in a Mix Presentation before mixing SHALL NOT exceed 28.
- There SHALL be at most 28 channels in total across all Audio Elements in the IA Sequence.

